Package: tableclothr
Title: Flexible Wrappers for Quickly Generating Static and Dynamic Tables
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Haniah", "Kring", , "hrishonkring@gmail.com", role = c("cre")),
    person("Josiah", "Ringelberg", , "Josiah.Ringelberg@gmail.com", role = c("aut")))
Description: A stream-lined and user-friendly R package that offers a set of flexible
             wrappers for effortless creation of static and dynamic tables. Designed with
             simplicity in mind, this package allows users to seamlessly generate themed
             gt and DT tables quickly without the need for complex and redundant coding.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    DT,
    gt,
    htmltools,
    htmlwidgets
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
